{"tid":1951807,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"志村健生前緋聞不絕！曾與AV女優談戀愛","createTime":"2020-03-31T08:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T10:22:28.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d4c295b0be2e408ea739cd882729caaa4de251b1","tid":1951807,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:02:37.000Z","msg":"終年70歲的日本喜劇演員志村健因新冠肺炎而病逝，然而，生前事跡在日內瞬間流出。原來志村建一生風流還跟石野陽子、優香、AV女優朝美穗香（Mihiro）和前主播加藤綾子等美女傳過緋聞，只可惜一家未能如願成家。其實志村健一直沒有放棄成家的念頭，他去年在節目上坦言，自己平均每3年換一任女友，多數都是以結婚為前提交往、同居，也很想要生個孩子，因為他認為「沒有小孩的話，我不就沒有存在的價值了嗎？」，更直言都已經這把年紀，但還享受戀愛的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/entertainment/news/【新冠肺炎】志村健生前緋聞不絕%ef%bc%81曾與av女優談戀愛/ar-BB11WNnp?ocid=spartandhp#image=BB11WBTE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fentertainment%2Fnews%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E5%BF%97%E6%9D%91%E5%81%A5%E7%94%9F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%8B%E8%81%9E%E4%B8%8D%E7%B5%95%25ef%25bc%2581%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87av%E5%A5%B3%E5%84%AA%E8%AB%87%E6%88%80%E6%84%9B%2Far-BB11WNnp%3Focid%3Dspartandhp%23image%3DBB11WBTE&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtBqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=17b03620\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/entertainment/news/【新冠肺炎】志村健生前緋聞不絕%ef%bc%81曾與av女優談戀愛/ar-BB11WNnp?ocid=spartandhp#image=BB11WBTE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545d74be31ebb9213b9156d30b08e84fe11a9686","tid":1951807,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:03:45.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"e8d025d355f3eeea5a46b4155b16ad75dc0ca1ae","tid":1951807,"uid":23848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"Mihiro正呀"},{"pid":"c41efdd59588008e4d24b69a1a3e20323a5b4a9f","tid":1951807,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"日本d搞笑藝人食好多女"},{"pid":"9c4fde9734d606219fa9d135ff7558efeb7dd95d","tid":1951807,"uid":7444,"